9 shippy comrades,
8 cool new fanfics,
7 music vids,
6 threads called 'Game',
FIVE THOUSAND POSTS! (I wish...)
A really cool sig,
Loads of mates,
A search engine called Venus,
AND A GATERS.NET FAMILY!!!

Merry Christmas, and please rate my song via the poll!
